(75, 1, '2012-02-26 20:00:23', '2012-02-26 20:00:23', '<strong>Vendor Information</strong>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Contact Market Coordinator, _______________________ or call 819-689 _______</p>\r\nAll vendors much be approved by provincial government authorities\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Health Unit Application Form</li>\r\n	<li>Chapeau Farmer’s Market Vendor’s Application Form</li>\r\n	<li>hapeau Farmer’s Market Rules and Regulations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur rules and entry forms are available as PDF files. Click <a href="http://get.adobe.com/reader/" target="_blank">here </a> to get Adbobe Acrobat Reader to view and print these files.\r\n\r\n<a>Provincial Health Unit Application Form PDF</a>\r\n\r\n<a>Farmer’s Market Vendor’s Application Form PDF</a>', 'Vendor Information', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vendor', '', '', '2012-03-09 17:12:24', '2012-03-09 17:12:24', '', 0, 'http://chapeau.phpfogapp.com/?page_id=75', 0, 'page', '', 0),
